<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>永旺 |一个思想的世界</title><link>https://aeon.co</link><description>Aeon 是一本关于思想和文化的杂志。我们发表深入的文章、精辟的文章以及原创和精选视频的组合——免费向所有人开放。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 03 Jul 2023 13:26:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>5124.灰键</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/the-extraordinary-story-of-a-black-holocaust-survivor-as-told-by-his-daughter?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="5124.灰键 |永旺视频" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/cc951920-35c0-4f3b-9041-902e42964912/show_5124greykey-landscape-6.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;一位黑人自由战士和大屠杀幸存者的女儿分享了她父亲深感辛酸、不可思议的人生故事&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/the-extraordinary-story-of-a-black-holocaust-survivor-as-told-by-his-daughter?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jul 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/the-extraordinary-story-of-a-black-holocaust-survivor-as-told-by-his-daughter?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>记住理查德·普莱斯！</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/remembering-the-18th-century-radical-dissenter-richard-price?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="记住理查德·普莱斯！ |永旺随笔" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/ee096b11-f7f2-4db3-9fe7-995805c46d1e/show_test-essay-46464001.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;这位 18 世纪的威尔士博学者因其激进的、不同的观点而被政治机构妖魔化，他应该得到更好的待遇&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——休·威廉姆斯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/remembering-the-18th-century-radical-dissenter-richard-price?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jul 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/remembering-the-18th-century-radical-dissenter-richard-price?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>享受的福音</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/chartreuse-economic-theology-and-the-french-spirit-of-capitalism?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="享受的福音 |永旺随笔" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/1f751c90-65d5-4e5b-b15a-fe876f37af1f/show_essay-gettyimages-2666507.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;法国人的美好生活理念并不总是具有合理的经济意义。对传统经济学来说更糟糕&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——查理·科尔曼&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/chartreuse-economic-theology-and-the-french-spirit-of-capitalism?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/chartreuse-economic-theology-and-the-french-spirit-of-capitalism?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>Voxel 实验室的音乐技术</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/electronic-gloves-and-even-potted-plants-make-music-in-a-playground-for-sound-innovation?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Voxel Lab 的音乐技术 |永旺视频" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/1e8a78f4-0244-41ff-9aa5-e6a1d0c0932f/show_music-tech-at-the-voxel-lab-landscape-5.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;进入麻省理工学院的体素实验室，学生们在这里制作奇怪的乐器，发出新颖的声音 - 甚至可能发现音乐的下一件大事&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/electronic-gloves-and-even-potted-plants-make-music-in-a-playground-for-sound-innovation?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/electronic-gloves-and-even-potted-plants-make-music-in-a-playground-for-sound-innovation?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>解开纠缠</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/our-simple-magic-free-recipe-for-quantum-entanglement?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="解开纠缠|永旺随笔" src="https://alpha.aeon.co/images/f6cf2e46-a840-42b5-91bc-c06e87ac5ae8/show_essay-final-gettyimages-1214210560.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;为什么量子世界会表现得如此奇怪、诡异？这是我们简单的四步解释（不需要魔法）&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;——休·普莱斯和肯·沃顿&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/our-simple-magic-free-recipe-for-quantum-entanglement?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/our-simple-magic-free-recipe-for-quantum-entanglement?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>审视生活：朱迪思·巴特勒和苏娜拉·泰勒</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/the-body-politics-a-philosophical-stroll-with-judith-butler-and-sunaura-taylor?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="审视生活：朱迪思·巴特勒和苏娜拉·泰勒 |永旺视频" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/b38d56d6-7415-4b60-8843-8fbb6c209f60/show_examined-life-judith-butler-and-sunaura-taylor-landscape-1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;身体在世界上意味着什么：与朱迪思·巴特勒和苏娜拉·泰勒一起在旧金山进行哲学漫步&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/the-body-politics-a-philosophical-stroll-with-judith-butler-and-sunaura-taylor?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/the-body-politics-a-philosophical-stroll-with-judith-butler-and-sunaura-taylor?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>镜像双胞胎的神话</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/what-do-twin-studies-really-say-about-identity-and-genetics?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="镜像双胞胎的神话|永旺随笔" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/9be46917-3245-493c-8b17-72e9366cd230/show_essay-par192375.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;关于遗传性、自我以及先天与后天之间由来已久的争论，双胞胎的生活告诉我们什么？&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;——加文·埃文斯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/what-do-twin-studies-really-say-about-identity-and-genetics?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/what-do-twin-studies-really-say-about-identity-and-genetics?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>世界还活着</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/the-grassroots-project-thats-restoring-an-endangered-hawaiian-ecosystem?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="奥拉卡霍努阿 |永旺视频" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/75a6fa61-460c-46fe-8c90-65a3408ef765/show_ola-ka-honua-landscape-2.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;在一个充满希望的生态恢复故事中，认识一个社区在火山斜坡上恢复生机的森林&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/the-grassroots-project-thats-restoring-an-endangered-hawaiian-ecosystem?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Jun 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/the-grassroots-project-thats-restoring-an-endangered-hawaiian-ecosystem?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>成为你所希望的</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/what-can-augustine-of-hippos-philosophy-teach-us-about-hope?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="成为你所希望的那样 |永旺随笔" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/9021ae40-2612-427a-9ff7-b061ea8b89d2/show_esssay-v4-rtxd63ts.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;面对全球挑战，奥古斯丁在悲观主义的绝望和乐观主义的假设之间提供了一条出路&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——迈克尔·兰姆&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/what-can-augustine-of-hippos-philosophy-teach-us-about-hope?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/what-can-augustine-of-hippos-philosophy-teach-us-about-hope?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>战争是怜悯和爱</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/what-crusaders-daggers-reveal-about-medieval-love-and-violence?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="战争是怜悯和爱 |永旺随笔" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/a5444139-94fb-415c-9a06-64c38b4b6dca/show_essay-final-akg5469206.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;骑士们参加十字军东征时携带的匕首帮助我们理解为什么他们认为圣战是一种爱的行为&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——威廉·切斯特·乔丹&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/what-crusaders-daggers-reveal-about-medieval-love-and-violence?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/what-crusaders-daggers-reveal-about-medieval-love-and-violence?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>自由游泳者</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/one-story-in-a-sea-of-millions-of-swimming-from-china-to-freedom-in-hong-kong?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="自由泳者|永旺视频" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/534796b5-c89a-4071-a9d8-27866c94f4c5/show_freedom-swimmer-landscape-2.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;一名“自由游泳者”从中国到香港的危险旅程——沿着200万人走过的路线&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/one-story-in-a-sea-of-millions-of-swimming-from-china-to-freedom-in-hong-kong?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Jun 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/one-story-in-a-sea-of-millions-of-swimming-from-china-to-freedom-in-hong-kong?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>重建多纳泰罗的雕塑</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/from-a-pencil-sketch-to-cherubs-dancing-in-stone-recreating-a-donatello-work?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="重建多纳泰罗的雕塑|永旺视频" src="https://alpha.aeon.co/images/7e6a33fe-7dd8-4f50-af16-c68f0a2c427d/show_recreating-donatellos-sculpture-landscape-4-v3.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;一位雕塑大师“啃咬”一块大理石，重现多纳泰罗浮雕中令人眼花缭乱的光影场景&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/from-a-pencil-sketch-to-cherubs-dancing-in-stone-recreating-a-donatello-work?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Jun 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/from-a-pencil-sketch-to-cherubs-dancing-in-stone-recreating-a-donatello-work?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>亚马逊儿童保育</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/why-runa-indigenous-people-find-natural-parenting-so-strange?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="亚马逊儿童保育|永旺随笔" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/eea1cd27-ead2-47aa-934a-f474cb9998f7/show_img_0124.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;在鲁纳人眼中，西方孩子在成长过程中被放纵、过度溺爱，无法面对外面的世界&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——弗朗西斯卡·梅泽扎纳&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/why-runa-indigenous-people-find-natural-parenting-so-strange?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/why-runa-indigenous-people-find-natural-parenting-so-strange?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>某种亲密感</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/toby-ponders-the-inner-lives-of-the-sheep-that-roam-atop-his-parents-graves?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="某种亲密感 |永旺视频" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/e72b0815-521f-486f-93f8-0a84d75cf268/show_some-kind-of-intimacy-landscape-1.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;对在什罗普郡墓地漫步的羊的失落和不可知的内心生活进行原创而深刻的思考&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/toby-ponders-the-inner-lives-of-the-sheep-that-roam-atop-his-parents-graves?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Jun 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/toby-ponders-the-inner-lives-of-the-sheep-that-roam-atop-his-parents-graves?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>这是蓝色食物</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/will-the-sustainable-food-of-the-future-come-from-the-blue?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="这是蓝色食物|永旺随笔" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/9cf2a585-efce-4be3-9737-60a6d34eb109/show_essay-final-gettyimages-944500300.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;考虑到社会和生态后果，海洋食物应该为数十亿人提供可持续的蛋白质&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——马杜拉·拉奥&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/will-the-sustainable-food-of-the-future-come-from-the-blue?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/will-the-sustainable-food-of-the-future-come-from-the-blue?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>卡夫卡日记</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/on-the-space-between-waking-and-dreaming-in-kafkas-diaries?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="卡夫卡日记|永旺随笔" src="https://epsilon.aeon.co/images/22148954-b027-4719-ae85-620253bb7df9/show_essay-v2-gettyimages-1425800389.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;白天，他是一名保险官员，晚上，他是一名不间断的、失眠的抄写员，记录着清醒和梦境之间的空间。&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;——罗斯·本杰明&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/on-the-space-between-waking-and-dreaming-in-kafkas-diaries?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/on-the-space-between-waking-and-dreaming-in-kafkas-diaries?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>布尔内沙</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/the-sworn-virgins-of-albania-who-trade-femininity-for-freedom?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="布尔内沙 |永旺视频" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/1b4fcb5b-6d09-420e-9561-defdaab328ea/show_burrnesha-landscape-3.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;对于阿尔巴尼亚的“宣誓处女”来说，在一个根深蒂固的父权社会中，穿着和行为像男人一样提供了一定程度的自主权&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/the-sworn-virgins-of-albania-who-trade-femininity-for-freedom?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Jun 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/the-sworn-virgins-of-albania-who-trade-femininity-for-freedom?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>所有可能的世界</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/multiple-worlds-has-been-given-artistic-impetus-by-physics?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="所有可能的世界 |永旺随笔" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/932375f1-695e-47d9-8534-6c26e4212ddc/show_essay-blow-aeon-art.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;长期以来，多重现实的想法一直是哲学思辨的问题，但物理学却赋予了新的艺术许可&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——蒂莫西·安徒生&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/multiple-worlds-has-been-given-artistic-impetus-by-physics?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/multiple-worlds-has-been-given-artistic-impetus-by-physics?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>我们可以在太空生孩子吗？</title><link>https://aeon.co/videos/would-children-born-beyond-earth-ever-be-able-to-return-to-humanitys-home-planet?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="我们可以在太空生孩子吗？ |永旺视频" src="https://omicron.aeon.co/images/f64eeb1f-a24e-491a-b046-3c197452d2a4/show_could-we-have-babies-in-space-landscape-2.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;一张来自火星的明信片，内容涉及在地球之外抚养孩子的后勤、遗传和伦理影响&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;- 永旺视频&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/videos/would-children-born-beyond-earth-ever-be-able-to-return-to-humanitys-home-planet?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Jun 2023 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/videos/would-children-born-beyond-earth-ever-be-able-to-return-to-humanitys-home-planet?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item><item><title>美国早期的亚洲人</title><link>https://aeon.co/essays/asians-were-visiting-the-west-coast-of-america-in-1587?utm_source=rss-feed</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="早期美国的亚洲人|永旺随笔" src="https://nu.aeon.co/images/4f7c0acb-646f-4bc3-aeb4-c165d0e3c91c/show_v1-essay-hessel-gerritsz-mar-del-sur.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 1587 年，亚洲水手来到美洲西海岸。一个世纪之内，他们在从墨西哥到秘鲁的殖民地定居下来&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;——迭戈·哈维尔·路易斯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://aeon.co/essays/asians-were-visiting-the-west-coast-of-america-in-1587?utm_source=rss-feed"&gt;在永旺读书&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Jun 2023 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://aeon.co/essays/asians-were-visiting-the-west-coast-of-america-in-1587?utm_source=rss-feed</guid></item></channel></rss>